================================================================================

OpenLumen is licensed under GPL-3.0-or-later.

Why GPL-3.0?
- Aligns with Red Moon (LibreShift/red-moon), which OpenLumen draws lineage from.
- Strong copyleft means any derivative that ships a binary must publish source —
  important for a system-level app that touches root drivers.
- Compatible with F-Droid's inclusion policies.

If you want a permissive license carve-out for a specific module, open an issue.
